 "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>Invoice</title>\n<style>\n    body {\n        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n        margin: 0;\n        padding: 0;\n    }\n\n    .container {\n        max-width: 800px;\n        margin: 0 auto;\n        padding: 20px;\n    }\n\n    .header {\n        text-align: left;\n        margin-bottom: 20px;\n    }\n\n    .logo-container {\n        display: flex;\n        justify-content: space-between;\n    }\n\n    .logo {\n        max-width: 200px;\n    }\n\n    .address {\n        font-size: 12px;\n    }\n\n    .letter {\n        text-align: center;\n        margin-top: 20px;\n    }\n    \n        .line {\n        margin-bottom: 2px;\n  text-align: left\n    }\n   .line2 {\n  margin-bottom:2px;\n  text-align: left\n    }\n\n    .labels {\n        display: inline-block;\n        width: 270px;\n  font-size: 12px\n    }\n\n    .colon {\n        margin-right: 10px;\n    }\n  .colon2 {\n        margin-right: 15px;\n    }\n  .colon3 {\n        margin-left: 80px;\n    }\n  .colon4 {\n        margin-left: 10px;\n    }\n  .section p {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-left: 20px;\n            text-indent: -20px; /* Negative text-indent to pull back the second line */\n        }\n        .footer {\n        background-color: #ff8a3a;\n        \n        padding: 5px;\n        text-align: center;\n        border: 1px solid #e8823d;\n    }\n\n    .footer-text {\n        font-weight: bold;\n  \t\tfont-size: 10px;\n        color: white;\n        display: inline-block;\n    }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\">\n            <p>Authorised Sales & Service Parts Dealer</p>\n            <div class=\"logo-container\">\n                <div>\n                    <img class=\"logo\" src=\"https://dcautoservices.mydotconsulting.com/files/perodua-logo.png\" alt=\"Company Logo 1\" width=\"200\">\n                    \n                </div>\n                <img class=\"logo\" src=\"https://dcautoservices.mydotconsulting.com/files/Screenshot%202024-04-28%20at%2011.30.35%20PM.png\" alt=\"Company Logo 2\" width=\"200\" height=\"45\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"letter\">\n                \n                 <p style=\"text-align: center;\">   <strong>INDIVIDUAL LETTER OF INDEMNITY</strong></p><br>\n                   <div class=\"line\">\n                    <span class=\"labels\">Date</span><span class=\"colon\">:</span>\n                    <span><b>{{ frappe.utils.formatdate(doc.date, \"dd MMMM yyyy\") }}</b></span>\n                </div>\n                   <br>\n                   <div class=\"line\">\n                    <span class=\"font-size:10px\">The Manager</span>\n                </div>\n                     <div class=\"line\">\n                    <span class=\"font-size:10px\">Malayan Banking Berhad</span>\n                </div>\n                 {% set bank_branch_doc = frappe.get_doc(\"Bank Branch\", doc.bank_branch) %}\n                     <div class=\"line\">\n                    <span style=\"font-size:13px;\">{{ bank_branch_doc.bank_branch }}</span>\n                </div>\n                     <br>\n                     <div class=\"line\">\n                    <span class=\"font-size:10px\">Dear sir,</span>\n                </div>\n                     <br>\n                <div class=\"line\">\n                    <span class=\"labels\">FLOOR STOCKING UNIT SERIAL NO</span><span class=\"colon2\">:</span>\n                    <span><b>{{doc.sola_number}}</b></span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"line\">\n                    <span class=\"labels\">HIRER NAME/NRIC NO</span><span class=\"colon2\">:</span>\n                    <span><b>{{doc.customer_name}}\n                    </b></span>\n                </div>\n                \n                   <div class=\"line2\">\n                    <span class=\"labels\">UNIT SERIAL NO. AMOUNT</span><span class=\"colon2\">:</span>\n                    <span >\n                      <b>RM {{ frappe.utils.fmt_money(doc.sola_amount, 2) }}\n                      </b></span>\n                </div>\n      <div class=\"line2\">\n                    <span class=\"labels\">HP LOAN AMOUNT</span><span class=\"colon2\">:</span>\n        <span ><b>RM {{ frappe.utils.fmt_money(doc.lou_loan_amount, 2) }}</b></span>\n                </div>\n               <div class=\"line2\">\n                    <span class=\"labels\">CHASSIS NO/ENGINE NO</span><span class=\"colon2\">:</span>\n                    <span><b>{{doc.chassis}}</b></span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"line2\">\n                    <span class=\"labels\">MODEL</span><span class=\"colon2\">:</span>\n                  <span ><b>{{doc.model}}</b></span>\n                </div><br>\n                       <hr style=\"\n    margin-top: -10px;\n    color: black;\n    border-top: 1px solid #000;\n\">\n<!--<hr style=\"-->\n<!--    margin-top: -18px;-->\n<!--    margin-bottom: 0px;-->\n<!--    color: black;-->\n<!--    border-top: 1px solid #000;-->\n<!--\">-->\n              \n   \n     \n                    \n      <p style=\"text-align: left;font-size:12px\">Please be advised that the above unit is under contra case against Floor Stocking (FS) at Auto Finance Centre Selayang.</p>\n         <p style=\"text-align: left;font-size:12px\">Kindly proceed to disburse the above amount to the FS AFC accordingly. We undertake to top-up any difference (shortfall) amount (if any).<br>In consideration of your releasing the FS e-Hakmilik Ownership Claim and security documents to enable us to transfer the vehicle to the hirer with your ownership claim, we hereby undertake the following:-</p>\n       \n         <br>           \n        <p style=\"text-align: left;font-size:12px\">1) To keep you indemnified against any losses that may be incurred by you in releasing the FS ownership claim and security documents to us.</p> \n           <p style=\"text-align: left;font-size:12px\">2) To forward you the Registration Card duly transferred to the hirer\u2019s name with your ownership \n    claim endorsed on it within 7days from the date FS ownership claim is released.</p> \n           <p style=\"text-align: left;font-size:12px\">3) To allow you to set-off any outstanding interest payable (to be computed up to HP disburse date) on the     above mentioned unit serial no./sola no. from the HP commission payable to us</p> \n           <p style=\"text-align: left;font-size:12px\">4) To settle with you the balance payable on the above mentioned unit serial no./sola no. if the Registration Card of the vehicle is not furnished to you within 7 days as required (Per para 2).</p> \n           <p style=\"text-align: left;font-size:12px\">5) We further undertake to pay any other charges payable in respect of the Floor Stocking financing of the above unit of vehicle (if any).</p> \n        \n              \n              <br>\n              <p style=\"text-align: left;font-size:12px;\">\n                    \n                    Thank you <br>\n                    \n                    Yours Sincerely,<br><br><br><br>\n                \n                -------------------------------------------- <br>\n                <b>AHMAD SYAIRAZI BIN SIDEK <br>\n                  DC AUTO SERVICES SDN BHD</b>\n                    \n                </p>\n              \n                 \n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"footer\">\n        <div class=\"footer-text\">\n            DC Auto Services Sdn Bhd (534274-P), Lot B3A-B7, Kawasan Perindustrian Batu Caves Utara, 68100, Batu Caves, Selangor D.E <br>Tel: 603-6250-9295 / 6259-1296\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n",
